messages.messageBody:
Hi all,
I just have to say hi to everyone. I've been off-line since Nov. We
have moved from San Diego to Michigan and I our computer was hooked
back up today, and this was the first place I had to come to. ;)

Our lives have completley changed in the past few months, Jason has
started school full time, I'm working for the first time in 8 years,
we have a small house with a backyard for the boys, a great
neighborhood with lots of kids, and we are expecting a new addition
to our family. Our lives are crazy, but wonderful.

I have soooooo much catching up to do, but I just had to say hi to
everyone.

~Rebecca
